Purpose
Encrypt all files in given directory path as well as all files in subfolders.


Usage

Call program with 2 arguments. First is mode which indicates whether to encrypt or decrypt specified 
directory by 'enc' or 'dec'.  Second argument is the full path in possix format.

ie.               *           * 
      node pv.js enc '/Users/Matt/Documents'


